# Install sandboxing app Firejail.

## Source: https://github.com/netblue30/firejail

## Add PPA repository for firejail
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:deki/firejail
sudo apt update

## Install dependencies
sudo apt install -y git build-essential libapparmor-dev pkg-config gawk

sudo apt install -y firejail
